text: Share 227 shares 'World (came) crashing down, everything changed,' Georgia said, but did not reveal the identity of her mystery ex. The TV personality also revealed she would stock her freezer with an 'embarrassing' amount of ice cream to help get through a split. 'My world came crashing down': Georgia did not reveal the identity of the mystery ex who broke her heart. Pictured with her current boyfriend, Lee Elliot Last month, Georgia was forced to deny rumours she and boyfriend Lee were the 'next to split' after fellow reality TV couple Sam Frost and Sasha Mielczarek broke up in December. Woman's Day's published an article alleging the pair had a 'blazing row' during an night out in Sydney. Lee was reportedly left 'sipping his Aperol Spritz' alone after Georgia 'stormed off' during dinner at the Da Orazio restaurant. Trouble in paradise?
